track_notes: Parked up and lifted my bike over the gate at The Loan. Rode it and pushed it on the steeper sections to old quarry at NY 5872 8058. Bike locked there - walked on to access land up ride. Then one fence to climb into the access land. Returned via Tod Crag, white knuckle ride down punctured on poorly graded track - tyre deflated just when gate was reached! This is the least visited of the English Marilyn Summits and one of the most remote.
track_title: Bike and walk route to Sighty Crag
